        <p>9.1. Unless agreed otherwise in writing, agreements are entered into for the duration stated in the quotation or order confirmation.</p>
        <p>9.2. Either party may terminate the agreement in writing with one month's notice, unless otherwise agreed.</p>
        <p>9.3. MS618 is entitled to dissolve the agreement with immediate effect if the Client is declared bankrupt, fails to fulfil its obligations, or circumstances come to light giving good reason to fear that performance will fail.</p>
        <p>9.4. Upon early termination by the Client, work already performed and costs already incurred are due. MS618 will draw up a final statement.</p>

